<p><strong>To Make a Request for Rapid Deployment Ministry Team help, please do the following:</strong></p>
<ol start="1">
<li><strong>Contact Pastor Joel Slater</strong> [ <script type='text/javascript'>var u1382630499='jslater'; var h43613624='pcctoday.com';var linktext='email';h43613624='pcctoday.com';document.write('<a href=' + 'mail' + 'to:' + u1382630499 + '@' + h43613624 + '>' + linktext + '</a>');
